From Greg Hennessy Subject Re Why not concentrate on child molesters In article cramer Clayton Cramer writes Yet when a law was proposed for Virginia that extended this philosophy to cigarette smokers so that people who smoked away from the work couldn't be discriminated against by employers the liberal Wilder vetoed Which shows that liberals don't give a damn about best person for the job it's just a power Of course Clayton ignores the fact that employers pay health insurance and insurance for smokers is more expensive than for non Greg Hennessy University of Virginia USPS Mail Astronomy Department Charlottesville VA USA Internet UUCP uunet virginia